<br>
Keep an open mind, and yes.. motrin does seem to be the root of all that is holy in military medicine =\.. that and foot powder.<br>
<br>
Make your decisions smartly, and you will perservere.<br>
<br>
Also, most ships (surf) are equipped with satellite relay classrooms, and most of those are free, where you can further / complete a degree if you wish.<br>
<br>
So i guess skimmers do have it a bit better.... sun (what's that), school, women, naaaahhhh nm that.. i wouldn't serve on a surface ship if they tripled my salary.  That's too much work.<br>
<br>
Take it as you will.  The military isn't for everyone, but for some, it's the open door to their future.<br>
<br>
Good Luck to you<br>
